description: A superb detached Victorian property on one of the town's finest roads, within easy reach of Barnes Village. The property has in excess of 6000 sq/ft of accommodation, a driveway and landscaped garden.

This impressive family home, which dates back to approximately 1840, offers original period features throughout and is set back from the road with off street parking for up to six cars and an original Coach House, which has been incorporated into the main house to provide further accommodation.

This house has been designed and built to an impeccable standard offering luxurious and elegant living. The accommodation is arranged over four floors comprising a large entrance hall, living room with tall sash windows, dining room, study and WC on the ground floor.

Discreetly situated a unique two storey period home enviably located on the corner of Krom Road and Recht Road offering seclusion and privacy. The house features a magnificent double height reception room with doors leading directly out onto a charming courtyard garden.
This luxurious three bedroom flat is contemporary in style and benefits from the use of a gymnasium and a reserved underground parking space.

Experience luxury living in the heart of Nairobi with this spacious and elegantly designed villa. Featuring modern amenities, breathtaking views, and a serene ambiance, this home is perfect for those seeking the ultimate urban retreat.

Embrace coastal living in this stunning beachfront property located in the vibrant city of Mombasa. Enjoy panoramic ocean views, direct beach access, and luxurious interiors designed for relaxation and entertainment.
Escape to the serene surroundings of Kisumu with this charming lakeside retreat. Nestled amidst lush greenery, this property offers tranquility, privacy, and breathtaking views of Lake Victoria.

Discover modern elegance and comfort in this stylish home located in the bustling city of Nakuru. Boasting spacious interiors, scenic views, and convenient access to amenities, this property is an urban oasis.

Experience the perfect blend of luxury and tranquility in this exquisite countryside estate located in Eldoret. Surrounded by lush gardens and picturesque landscapes, this property offers a peaceful retreat from city life.

Indulge in contemporary urban living with this stylish apartment situated in the heart of Nairobi's bustling Westlands neighborhood. Featuring sleek design, modern amenities, and panoramic city views, this property offers the ultimate cosmopolitan lifestyle.

Relax and unwind in this exclusive beachfront villa nestled along the pristine shores of Diani Beach, offering unrivaled privacy, personalized service, and direct access to the turquoise waters of the Indian Ocean.
